import React from "react";
import { Nav } from "react-bootstrap";
import Logo from "./img/logo"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom";
import Estudios from "./Estudios";
import Skills from "./Skills";
import Proyectos from "./Proyectos";
import Experiencia from "./Experiencia";

class Navbar extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Router>
          <Nav
            variant="tabs"
            defaultActiveKey="/home"
            className="justify-content-center h6 p-3 "
          >
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/" className="text-success" id="nav1">
                Home
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/estudios" className="text-success" id="nav1">
                Estudios
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/skills" className="text-success">
                Skills
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/proyectos" className="text-success">
                Proyectos
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link as={Link} to="/experiencia" className="text-success">
                Experiencia
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
          </Nav>

          <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/estudios" component={Estudios} />
            <Route exact path="/skills" component={Skills} />
            <Route exact path="/proyectos" component={Proyectos} />
            <Route exact path="/experiencia" component={Experiencia} />
          </Switch>
        </Router>
      </React.Fragment>
    );
  }
}

export default Navbar;
